# Design System

## Brand Colors (CSS variables — never hardcode inline)
--brand-dark: #0c3a30
--brand-accent: #9edd05
--brand-light: #edf1ee
--brand-card: #fffaeb

## Fonts
Headings: Outfit (font-display)
Body: Inter Tight

## CSS Classes (globals.css — never recreate)
.charm-card · .btn-primary · .btn-accent · .btn-outline
.section-label · .gradient-text · .accent-underline
.stats-badge · .section-ptb · .shape-blob
.animate-float · .animate-float-slow · .animate-rotation
.animate-fadeinup · .reveal · .delay-100 through .delay-400

## Section Backgrounds
Dark hero: style={{ background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #082720 0%, #0c3a30 100%)' }}
Dark CTA: style={{ background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #082720 0%, #0c3a30 50%, #0f4a3d 100%)' }}
Light section: className="bg-brand-light"
Card background: className="bg-brand-card"

## Dark Section Overrides
section-label: !border-white/20 !bg-white/10 !text-brand-accent
btn-outline white: !text-white !border-white/40 !shadow-none
  hover:!bg-white hover:!text-brand-dark hover:!border-white

## Rules
- Never use .reveal on static server pages
- Never recreate classes already in globals.css
- Never use Finto CSS classes, data-aos, data-cues, or Remixicon
- All icons use lucide-react
- All internal links use next/link Link component
- All images use next/image Image component
- Cards use rounded-[20px] or rounded-[24px]
